These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, librarian
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, turkish
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, aristoff
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the turkish##3
2. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
3. the librarian is the person who growsorchid##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Flower      | orchid  | poppy   |
| Job   | librarian     | social-worker   |
| Nationality         | turkish | argentine |
| Cigar     | baccarat | aristoff    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
House: colonial, modern
City: boston, miami
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, coral
1. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is the person who likes coral##1
3. the modern house is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| House          | colonial     | modern |
| City   | miami | boston  |
| Music-Genre           | hip-hop         | ambient     |
| Color     | apricot   | coral    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, june
There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, white
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Birthday    | june     | may |
| Color         | white | ebony    |
| Sport         | water-polo         | weightlifting        |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop         | d&b    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
