2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Sport      | golf     | soccer |
| Birthday          | july   | december  |
| Flower         | dahlia | daisy     |
| Cigar   | ritmeester  | davidoff         |

