3. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the modern house is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Birthday           | november | december    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower       | daffodil |
| House           | modern         | cottage    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing    | fishing   |

