2. the person who likes yellow is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Pet         | hedgehog   | cat |
| Birthday           | march | december    |
| Color   | yellow      | blue         |
| Cigar         | blend   | fonseca |

