.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, dubstep
2 different games are played: chess, domino
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, peach
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, camping
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Music-Genre    | techno | dubstep    |
| Game         | domino        | chess |
| Food         | pomegranate          | peach     |
| Hobby   | photography        | camping     |

 